text: Anshun () is a prefecture-level city of Guizhou province, near the location of Huangguoshu Waterfall, the tallest in China. As of 2010, it had a population of 2,297,339. Census 2010 The city is known for its aerospace industry.Anshun opens flights to Chongqing and Beijing ==References== Category:Cities in China Category:Lists of cities in Asia Category:Guizhou
